    "Additionally, integrating lower-fineness SCMs with more reactive SCMs, such as SF and MK, can help balance improvements in strength and durability.",
    "Finally, optimizing mix design by adjusting the water-to-binder ratio can further refine material performance, enhancing the overall effectiveness of the composite.",
    "The following Table 13 shows fineness and effects of (SCMs) on concrete properties.",
    "Sustainability and cost efficiencyThe environmental and economic benefits of using SCMs in cement-based material production have been widely explored by researchers.",
    "For instance, in the United Kingdom, incorporating 400,000 tons of FA into concrete has been shown to reduce annual CO₂ emissions by approximately 250,000 tons."
